         MACRO                                                          00160000
.*                                                                      00170000
.* This macro creates a nested control block within another one         00180000
.*                                                                      00190000
&LABEL   NESTCB &CB,                   * Nested control block id       *00200000
               &TYPE,                  * Type - defaults to hex        *00210000
               &PRFX,                  * Prefix to use if label blank  *00220000
               &INIT=,                 * Initialization value          *00230000
               &LEN=                   * Length in parentheses          00240000
.********************************************************************** 00241001
